metadata.name: Cryptodragonies #1
metadata.description: The Cryptosdragonies is a collection of 10,000 unique NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain, it’s based on the ERC-721 standard.Each mythical Cryptodragonies holds unstoppable power, the ability to breathe fire and kill his enemies. Build your little dragon’s army and conquer the earth! Watch out for the knights, wizards, elves, and many mythical creatures along the way. Try and collect them, and maybe you’ll be lucky enough to get the GOLD legendary dragons! Your Cryptodragonies NFTs membership will grant you access to our members-only benefits. For example, you’ll have access to future free NFT drops areas and cool perks that can only be unlocked within our community, check it out! https://cryptodragonies.com
